有人叫其他口號，現場嘈雜，相信並非所有在場人士都能聽到當時所有人所說的所有事。他說，當日有被捕人的懷孕妻子跌倒，有女警立刻照顧安慰。鄧炳強說，他對孕婦表示慰問，而事件有人投訴，投訴警察課正調查，他不談細節。<br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強又說，9月6日旺角有人參與未經批准集結，警方要截查一班人，有少女突然拔足狂奔，這項可疑舉措令警員有責任將她截停，用最低武力截停及制服，知道她只有12歲後就馬上安排女警照顧，事件同樣有人投訴，投訴警察課正處理。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:25:05.000Z","msg":"差佬形象差劣，成班小醜自說自話。"},{"pid":"50382cca2cf0b0a52efe9eefcdd438bd7a36a205","tid":2222610,"uid":181155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:27:45.000Z","msg":"小朋友周街跑跑跳跳又要拉？"},{"pid":"3491589baec1078e838f846d3a4d1347234bd44b","tid":2222610,"uid":265917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:28:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rMw7zzE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrMw7zzE.png&h=6d9b9c8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9c5jFJB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9c5jFJB.png&h=13cb05e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v7sZqGA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv7sZqGA.png&h=cf0e3bfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">最簡單既嘢偏偏最少人做</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"902224fed227f58ec2715fa4f4346a550f5c6988","tid":2222610,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:28:30.000Z","msg":"個個人面獸心仲要full gear 你唔撚驚就怪"},{"pid":"7447562f937849ca84fcedca5825b24066a96124","tid":2222610,"uid":215341,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:28:49.000Z","msg":"我走又係比你拉，我唔走又係比你拉，咁點解我唔走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d23a098d0f609f7f5548fe49ff4c37579b1d756","tid":2222610,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea70c8ae11b73bbf63acc9a3f4a43ccb4c305955","tid":